description:
We are looking for a motivated 
Middle/Senior C# (Remote) for future positions.
 
Our client is a multinational technology company renowned for its cutting-edge software, hardware, and services.
 
Key Responsibilities:
- Write and test C# code;
- Collaborate with the team to solve coding challenges and complete project tasks;
- Work with SQL databases to create and optimize queries;
- Explore DevOps practices and tools to improve the development workflow.

requirements:
Requirements:
- 4 years of experience in commercial software development;
- Problem-solving skills and troubleshooting skills;
- Proficient in C# programming language and .Net Framework;
- Knowledge of Cloud Computing principles and practices (Azure);
- Excellent written and verbal communication skills in English;
- Experience with MSSQL;
 
Nice to have:
- Experience with Azure Pipelines;
- Experience with CosmosDB;
- Experience with Kusto;
 
Working Conditions:
- Full CET overlap;
- B2B contract with paid vacation, sick leave, and public holidays;
- Supportive learning environment with mentorship from experienced developers;
- We have offices in Egypt, Kazakhstan, Georgia and Armenia strategically located, technically well-equipped, and ready for your work.
